<HEAD>Third Time in Three Days, Mystery Man Hands Out $50 Bills</HEAD>
<DATELINE>DETROIT (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   It's beginning to look like a daily habit _ a man
in a white tuxedo hops out of a limousine and spends a couple of
